title: Ore no Otouto no Hajimete no Onedari
original_name: おれの弟のはじめてのおねだり
sinopse:
1-2. Ore no Otouto to Honjitsu no Himegoto (My Little Brother and Today's Secret)
3-4. Ore no Otouto no Hajimete no Onedari (The First Thing My Little Brother Ever Begged For) 5. Maru-kun to oo Yattemita. (I Tried It With Maru) 6. Untitled
